---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import cover from "../assets/book-front-cover-angle.png";
import creature from "../assets/veilhost_creature_lurks.png";
---

<Layout title="The Veilhost Trilogy | Available 31st July">
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="page-shell hero-grid">
			<div class="hero-copy">
				<p class="kicker">Book One of the Veilhost Trilogy</p>
				<h1>The Creatures Lurk</h1>
				<p class="byline">By Topher Knowles</p>
				<p class="coming-soon">Available on Kindle and in Paperback 31st July</p>
				<form class="subscribe-form" action="/api/subscribe" method="post">
					<label for="email">Subscribe for updates</label>
					<div class="form-row">
						<input id="email" name="email" type="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required />
						<button type="submit">Notify me</button>
					</div>
					<label class="subscribe-trap" for="website">Website</label>
					<input
						class="subscribe-trap"
						id="website"
						name="website"
						type="text"
						tabindex="-1"
						autocomplete="off"
					/>
				</form>
			</div>
			<div class="cover-stage" aria-label="Featured book cover">
				<img src={cover.src} alt="Angled front cover for The Veilhost Trilogy" class="book-cover" />
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="synopsis page-shell" aria-labelledby="synopsis-title">
		<div class="synopsis-art">
			<img src={creature.src} alt="" loading="lazy" />
		</div>
		<div class="synopsis-copy">
			<p class="kicker">Synopsis</p>
			<h2 id="synopsis-title">Some wonders can be mistaken for monsters</h2>
			<p>
				Beyond Matrika’s guarded walls, a neighbouring kingdom has fallen to an enemy no survivor can explain. Now that silent force is moving south: pale warriors who strike without warning, and leave only rumours in their wake. Desperate to defend his people, Matrika’s king turns to forgotten legends, hoping myth can succeed where armies may fail.
			</p>
			<p>
				As war draws closer, creatures glimpsed only in fragments, beautiful and terrifying, caught somewhere between nature, myth, and miracle begin to emerge. To survive what is coming, the Veilhost must discover which stories were meant to frighten them, and which were meant to awaken them.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="chapter-banner" aria-labelledby="chapters-banner-title">
		<div class="page-shell banner-inner">
			<div>
				<p class="kicker">Start reading</p>
				<h2 id="chapters-banner-title">Read The First 3 Chapters</h2>
			</div>
			<a class="btn" href="/chapters/">Open preview</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.hero {
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
		padding: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 5rem) 0 clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(8, 7, 5, 0.95), rgba(8, 7, 5, 0.72));
		color: var(--color-white);
	}

	.hero-grid {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.95fr) minmax(280px, 1.05fr);
		align-items: center;
		gap: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 5rem);
	}

	.hero-copy {
		max-width: 560px;
	}

	.kicker {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		letter-spacing: 0.12em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	h1 {
		margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
		font-size: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 9.5rem);
	}

	.byline {
		margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
		font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.2vw, 1.45rem);
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	.coming-soon {
		display: inline-block;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		border-block: 2px solid currentColor;
		padding: 0.35rem 0;
		font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 4vw, 2rem);
		font-weight: 900;
		line-height: 1;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	.subscribe-form {
		max-width: 520px;
	}

	.subscribe-trap {
		position: absolute;
		left: -9999px;
		width: 1px;
		height: 1px;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.subscribe-form label {
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	.form-row {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
		gap: 0.55rem;
	}

	input {
		min-height: 3rem;
		border: 2px solid var(--color-white);
		background: var(--color-white);
		padding: 0 0.9rem;
		color: var(--color-black);
	}

	button {
		min-height: 3rem;
		border: 2px solid var(--color-white);
		background: var(--color-ember);
		padding: 0 1rem;
		color: var(--color-black);
		font-weight: 900;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		cursor: pointer;
		transition:
			background-color 180ms ease,
			transform 180ms ease;
	}

	button:hover {
		background: var(--color-white);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

	.cover-stage {
		position: relative;
		isolation: isolate;
		animation: cover-rise 800ms ease both;
	}

	.cover-stage::before {
		content: "";
		position: absolute;
		inset: 14% 8% 8% 16%;
		z-index: -1;
		background: rgba(217, 131, 39, 0.52);
		filter: blur(34px);
		transform: rotate(-6deg);
	}

	.book-cover {
		width: min(100%, 620px);
		margin-inline: auto;
		filter: drop-shadow(28px 28px 22px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.48));
		transform-origin: 50% 80%;
		animation: cover-float 5.5s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	.synopsis {
		position: relative;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(190px, 0.38fr) minmax(0, 0.62fr);
		gap: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
		align-items: center;
		padding: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6rem) 0;
	}

	.synopsis-art {
		align-self: stretch;
		min-height: 360px;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.synopsis-art img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: contain;
		object-position: center bottom;
		opacity: 0.82;
		mix-blend-mode: luminosity;
	}

	.synopsis-copy {
		background: var(--color-white);
		padding: clamp(1.25rem, 4vw, 3rem);
		box-shadow: 12px 12px 0 var(--color-black);
	}

	.synopsis h2,
	.chapter-banner h2 {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 4vw, 5.8rem);
	}

	.synopsis p:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.chapter-banner {
		padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem) 0;
		background: var(--color-white);
	}

	.banner-inner {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.chapter-banner h2 {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	@keyframes cover-rise {
		from {
			opacity: 0;
			transform: translateY(24px) rotate(-1deg);
		}

		to {
			opacity: 1;
			transform: translateY(0) rotate(0);
		}
	}

	@keyframes cover-float {
		0%,
		100% {
			transform: translateY(0) rotate(-0.5deg);
		}

		50% {
			transform: translateY(-12px) rotate(0.5deg);
		}
	}

	@keyframes ember-pulse {
		0%,
		100% {
			opacity: 0.55;
			transform: scale(1);
		}

		50% {
			opacity: 0.9;
			transform: scale(1.08);
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 820px) {
		.hero-grid,
		.synopsis {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.hero-copy {
			max-width: none;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.form-row,
		.banner-inner {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: stretch;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.synopsis-art {
			min-height: 280px;
		}
	}
</style>
